data.description: MULTIPLE OFFERS...SUBMIT YOUR HIGHEST AND BEST BY 3PM ON 12/20/23! THIS IS A SHORT SALE! Take a tour of this home before it's SOLD! This 3 bedroom 3 and 1/2 bath GOLF COURSE POOL HOME IS AVAILABLE TODAY! As you drive the exceptional Sun N Lakes of Sebring community you'll be wowed by the perfectly manicured championship golf courses, community center, recreational pool, walking paths, manicured landscaping, and you will know you found your FLORIDA PARADISE! As you pull into the drive way, you will be taken back by the lush landscaping with an assortment of wild plants, shrubs, and trees. Going through the front door, you'll notice the open and bright central living area adjacent to the LARGE POOL AND OPEN KITCHEN! Additional features include: NEW ROOF, NEW AC, FRESH EXTERIOR PAINT, split floor plan, tile flooring, in house utility, and the property is located on almost a half acre! This is your one opportunity to own a FLORIDA POOL HOME ON THE GOLF COURSE WITH RELAXING VIEWS ALL AROUND in the warm weather. This home is perfect for a family, part time resident, or first time buyer. Call today see your new home today!
